OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FThe sudden closure of a care home for
OL,8,Fvulnerable residents with dementia
OL,9,F'must never happen again', a review
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FHazel Garth Care Home in Knottingley,
OL,13,Fwas closed by Wakefield Council in May
OL,14,F2024, leaving six families with just a
OL,15,Fday to prepare their elderly relatives
OL,16,Ffor eviction.
OL,18,FMost were picked up in taxis the
OL,19,Ffollowing day and moved into
OL,20,Falternative accommodation.
