OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FThe 30-page report described how one
OL,8,Fresident died 16 days after being
OL,9,Fmoved.
OL,11,FThe independent review found the
OL,12,Fclosure "should not have happened in
OL,13,Fthe way it did" and highlighted the
OL,14,F"harm and distress" caused to
OL,15,Fresidents, their families and all the
OL,16,Fstaff.
OL,18,FIt added there wasn't enough focus on
OL,19,Fthe needs of residents.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
