OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FThe investigation also found failings
OL,8,Fin leadership and management, and
OL,9,Finformation was not shared with
OL,10,Ffamilies, staff, and senior
OL,11,Fpoliticians which they needed to know.
OL,13,FIt said decisions, including the
OL,14,Fmoving of residents from their homes
OL,15,Fwithin a 24 ` 48 hour period, were
OL,16,F"not justified."
OL,18,FThe council has since apologised for
OL,19,Fits failings.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
