OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FIt's Leader, Cllr Denise Jeffery,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I'm deeply sorry to the
OL,9,Fresidents, their families, and our
OL,10,Fstaff at Hazel Garth for the impact
OL,11,Fthis decision had on them.
OL,13,F"I've listened to some extremely
OL,14,Fdistressing stories from the families.
OL,15,FThe extent to which we let them down
OL,16,Fis starkly set out in the independent
OL,17,Freport. And the seriousness of the
OL,18,Ffailings underlines how this must
OL,19,Fnever be allowed to happen again."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
