OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FJanet Waggott, who carried out the
OL,8,Freview said she is "reassured" by
OL,9,Faction that has since been taken by
OL,10,Fthe council.
OL,12,FShe also called for compensation to be
OL,13,Fpaid for the distress caused to
OL,14,Fresidents and their families.
OL,16,FWakefield Council said it had already
OL,17,Ftaken "proactive improvement steps"
OL,18,Fincluding apologising to residents'
OL,19,Ffamilies, and strengthening leadership
OL,20,Fin adult social care.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
