OL,3,C'Must never happen again': Review
OL,4,Cfinds failings in dementia care home
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FThere has been an overhaul of the
OL,8,Fleadership of it's adult social care
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FIn June, the council confirmed that Jo
OL,12,FWebster, the corporate director for
OL,13,Fadults, health and communities, had
OL,14,Fstepped down.
OL,16,FThe review, which took seven weeks,
OL,17,Fwas commissioned jointly by the Leader
OL,18,Fand Chief Executive of the council a
OL,19,Fmonth after the care home closure.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
